---
title: Jerk Chicken & Veggie Traybake with Charred Corn Salsa
description: We're taking a leaf out of the Jamaicans' book with this easy-going chicken traybake, flavoured with our signature jerk seasoning. Pop it in the oven, then take your time making a corn salsa and punchy yoghurt for a fuss-free meal with plenty of mojo.
